body:
expected behavior
 sync to continue or error out with proper error

actual behavior
 sync hangs for several hours -- several errors in log but sync never completes

steps to reproduce
 customer has the following:
 owncloud server: 5.0.11 on debian 6.0.7 64bit
 owncloud client: 1,4.0 on debian wheezy 64bit kde

they have 2 folders set up to be synced.

both folders were syncing well for a while, then one folder started to error out and sync never completed on this folder. sync starts at 7:51 and the sync is error out at 11:01am.


client logs were looked at by @dragotin and it was found that there is an internal server error.


owncloud logs shows the following: 

